"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 13, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104alw1665702731087.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/alw1665702731087.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/alw1665702731087.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"alw1665702731087\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      ODBC Connector Options\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"alw1665702731087__odbc_connector_options_162531\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">You can assign connector options by setting <code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$OD</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">x</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">_PARAMS</code> in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"alw1665702731087__topic_d54347e1_d54348e1_d54349e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54350e1_d54351e1_d54352e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$OD</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">x</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">_PARAMS</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var>\n            n}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"alw1665702731087__topic_d35937e1_d35938e1_d35939e1_d35940e1_d35941e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d804752e87\">\n                        \n Options\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25139e1_d25140e1_d25141e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54356e1_d54357e1_d54358e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lca1665702725226.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lca1665702725226.html\" title=\"Enable or disable testing for the existence of tables and stored procedures.\">checks</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25142e1_d25143e1_d25144e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54359e1_d54360e1_d54361e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sgu1665702731162.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sgu1665702731162.html\" title=\"Specify the file containing the data type specification.\">data types</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25145e1_d25146e1_d25147e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54362e1_d54363e1_d54364e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wzs1665702731233.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wzs1665702731233.html\" title=\"Map dates to timestamps\">date as timestamp</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25148e1_d25149e1_d25150e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54365e1_d54366e1_d54367e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fug1665702705112.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fug1665702705112.html\" title=\"Set the default locking strategy employed by Uniface.\">default locking</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25151e1_d25152e1_d25153e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54368e1_d54369e1_d54370e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xcw1665702729440.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xcw1665702729440.html\" title=\"Specifies the case for table names.\">entity names</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25154e1_d25155e1_d25156e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54371e1_d54372e1_d54373e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dqd1665702725479.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dqd1665702725479.html\" title=\"Specify the maximum size of field names.\">field name size</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25157e1_d25158e1_d25159e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54374e1_d54375e1_d54376e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xti1665702725693.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xti1665702725693.html\" title=\"Specify whether statements remain open after a commit.\">hold statements</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25160e1_d25161e1_d25162e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54377e1_d54378e1_d54379e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"due1665702952441.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/due1665702952441.html\" title=\"Specify whether identifiers should be quoted.\">identifiers</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25163e1_d25164e1_d25165e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54380e1_d54381e1_d54382e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rmo1665702729638.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rmo1665702729638.html\" title=\"Case for table and column names\">identifier case</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25166e1_d25167e1_d25168e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54383e1_d54384e1_d54385e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"edv1665702731303.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/edv1665702731303.html\" title=\"Set the character to use as quotation mark for identifiers.\">identifier quote char</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25169e1_d25170e1_d25171e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54386e1_d54387e1_d54388e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"auj1665702731375.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/auj1665702731375.html\" title=\"Specify the syntax of indexes and primary keys.\">key syntax</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25172e1_d25173e1_d25174e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54389e1_d54390e1_d54391e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zxo1665702731450.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zxo1665702731450.html\" title=\"Set the logon timeout.\">logon timeout</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25175e1_d25176e1_d25177e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54392e1_d54393e1_d54394e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ucl1665702952795.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ucl1665702952795.html\" title=\"Use specific data mapping of version U3.0\">mapping</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25178e1_d25179e1_d25180e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54395e1_d54396e1_d54397e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ygi1665702731521.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ygi1665702731521.html\" title=\"Specify whether the database supports non-null columns.\">non null columns</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25184e1_d25185e1_d25186e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54401e1_d54402e1_d54403e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vlq1665702953081.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vlq1665702953081.html\" title=\"Specify the maximum record size.\">record size</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25187e1_d25188e1_d25189e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54404e1_d54405e1_d54406e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"exm1665702661663.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/exm1665702661663.html\" title=\"Set the number of rows the connector selects from the DBMS in each step of the Uniface stepped hitlist.\">step size</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25190e1_d25191e1_d25192e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54407e1_d54408e1_d54409e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bdu1665702727695.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bdu1665702727695.html\" title=\"Sets the maximum size of table names in the database.\">table name size</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25193e1_d25194e1_d25195e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54410e1_d54411e1_d54412e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kem1665702731596.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kem1665702731596.html\" title=\"Map times to timestamps.\">time as timestamp</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"alw1665702731087__topic_d35942e1_d35943e1_d35944e1_d35945e1_d35946e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d804752e333\">\n                        \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54416e1_d54417e1_d54418e1\">Most connector options are enable options; a specific feature is enabled by setting the option. Some options have a numeric parameter (a nonnegative decimal integer). Each numeric option has a default value, although the range of valid values is option-specific.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"alw1665702731087__topic_d35947e1_d35948e1_d35949e1_d35950e1_d35951e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d804752e342\">\n                        \n Syntax Rules\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54422e1_d54423e1_d54424e1\">The syntax rules for <code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$OD</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">x</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">_PARAMS</code> are:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25196e1_d25197e1_d25198e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54425e1_d54426e1_d54427e1\">Each option may be specified only once</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25199e1_d25200e1_d25201e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54428e1_d54429e1_d54430e1\">Multiple options must be separated by commas (<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>)</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25202e1_d25203e1_d25204e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54431e1_d54432e1_d54433e1\">For specifying multiple options, you can use the short format</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25205e1_d25206e1_d25207e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54434e1_d54435e1_d54436e1\">Words and numbers within each option are separated by one or more spaces or tabs</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25208e1_d25209e1_d25210e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54437e1_d54438e1_d54439e1\">Options are not case-dependent</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"alw1665702731087__li_d25211e1_d25212e1_d25213e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54440e1_d54441e1_d54442e1\">All options have the form <var class=\"keyword varname\">Directive</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>. Instead of the equal sign (<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>), a colon can be used. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">USYS$OD0_PARAMS = step : 20, default locking = O</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"alw1665702731087__topic_d35952e1_d35953e1_d35954e1_d35955e1_d35956e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d804752e419\">\n                        \n ODBCCONF Settings and ODBC Options\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"alw1665702731087__p_d54446e1_d54447e1_d54448e1\">The previous ODBC Connector had a configuration tool called <code class=\"ph codeph\">ODBCCONF</code>, which has been replaced by new configuration utilities <span class=\"ph filepath\">uodbccfg.exe</span> (for version U4.0) and <span class=\"ph filepath\">uodbccfg41.exe</span> (for version U4.1). The following tables show the old ODBCCONF settings and their equivalent ODBC options in the Uniface ODBC Connector.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">ODBCCONF Settings Mapped to ODBC Options</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">ODBCCONF Setting</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">ODBCCONF Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">ODBC Option Name</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">ODBC Option Value</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Index type</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Datasource (default)</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Paradox tables</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Foxpro tables</p>\n<p class=\"p\">DOS file system</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">key syntax</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">index</code> (default)</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">paradox</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">foxpro</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">dosfile</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Primary key clause</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Constraint</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Primary key</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">key syntax</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">See Index type</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">constraint</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">primary key</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Table / Column case</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Uppercase / Lowercase</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">identifier case</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">upper</code> (default) / <code class=\"ph codeph\">lower</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Map dates to timestamps</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">date as timestamp</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code> (default) / <code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Map times to timestamps</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">time as timestamp</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code> (default) / <code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Limits of  tables</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\"> statements</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5060e1_d5061e1_d5062e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Implicit ODBCCONF Settings Mapped to ODBC options</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">ODBCCONF Setting</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">ODBCCONF Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">ODBC Option Name</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">ODBC Option Value</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Identifier quote character</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">identifier quote char</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">Commonly <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code> (double quote) or <code class=\"ph codeph\">'</code> (single quote)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">table name size</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">Maximum size of table name</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">field name size</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">Maximum size of field name</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">non-null columns</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">record size</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">Maximum size of record (row)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">identifiers</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5063e1_d5064e1_d5065e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">quoted</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">unquoted</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5066e1_d5067e1_d5068e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Obsolete ODBCCONF Settings</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5066e1_d5067e1_d5068e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">ODBCCONF Setting</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5066e1_d5067e1_d5068e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">ODBCCONF Value</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5066e1_d5067e1_d5068e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Commit on create table</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5066e1_d5067e1_d5068e1__entry__2\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5066e1_d5067e1_d5068e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Character dates as YYMMDD</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5066e1_d5067e1_d5068e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">On / Off</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5066e1_d5067e1_d5068e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Date base date</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"alw1665702731087__table_d5066e1_d5067e1_d5068e1__entry__2\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/msq1665702542189.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>[DRIVER_SETTINGS]</a><p>Use the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file to specify the database and component engine connectors used, and their parameter options. The options available depend on the connector in use.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525761\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525761\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ODBC Connector Options Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 13, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 ODBC Connector Options You can assign connector options by setting USYS$OD x _PARAMS in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file. USYS$OD x _PARAMS Option { , Option n} Options checks data types date as timestamp default locking entity names field name size hold statements identifiers identifier case identifier quote char key syntax logon timeout mapping non null columns record size step size table name size time as timestamp Description Most connector options are enable options; a specific feature is enabled by setting the option. Some options have a numeric parameter (a nonnegative decimal integer). Each numeric option has a default value, although the range of valid values is option-specific. Syntax Rules The syntax rules for USYS$OD x _PARAMS are: Each option may be specified only once Multiple options must be separated by commas ( , ) For specifying multiple options, you can use the short format Words and numbers within each option are separated by one or more spaces or tabs Options are not case-dependent All options have the form Directive = Value . Instead of the equal sign ( = ), a colon can be used. For example: USYS$OD0_PARAMS = step : 20, default locking = O Copy ODBCCONF Settings and ODBC Options The previous ODBC Connector had a configuration tool called ODBCCONF , which has been replaced by new configuration utilities uodbccfg.exe (for version U4.0) and uodbccfg41.exe (for version U4.1). The following tables show the old ODBCCONF settings and their equivalent ODBC options in the Uniface ODBC Connector. Table 1. ODBCCONF Settings Mapped to ODBC Options ODBCCONF Setting ODBCCONF Value ODBC Option Name ODBC Option Value Index type Datasource (default) Paradox tables Foxpro tables DOS file system key syntax index (default) paradox foxpro dosfile Primary key clause None Constraint Primary key key syntax See Index type constraint primary key Table / Column case Uppercase / Lowercase identifier case upper (default) / lower Map dates to timestamps date as timestamp on (default) / off Map times to timestamps time as timestamp on (default) / off Limits of tables Number statements Number Table 2. Implicit ODBCCONF Settings Mapped to ODBC options ODBCCONF Setting ODBCCONF Value ODBC Option Name ODBC Option Value Identifier quote character — identifier quote char Commonly \" (double quote) or ' (single quote) — — table name size Maximum size of table name — — field name size Maximum size of field name — — non-null columns on or off — — record size Maximum size of record (row) — — identifiers quoted or unquoted Table 3. Obsolete ODBCCONF Settings ODBCCONF Setting ODBCCONF Value Commit on create table Character dates as YYMMDD On / Off Date base date Related Links [DRIVER_SETTINGS] Use the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file to specify the database and component engine connectors used, and their parameter options. The options available depend on the connector in use. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}